 \sum_{k=0}^{\lfloor n/2\rfloor}2^{-2nk}\binom{n}{2k}\binom{2k}{k}^{\large n} \sim1+\binom{n}{2}(1/2)^n+O\left(n^4(3/8)^n\right)\tag{3} 
